com.skobbler.ngx.positioner
Class SKPosition

java.lang.Object
  com.skobbler.ngx.positioner.SKPosition
Direct Known Subclasses:
SKExtendedRoutePosition
public class SKPosition
extends java.lang.Object

A data class representing a geographic position. A position can consist of a latitude, longitude, and other information such as heading, accuracy and speed.

Version:
3.0
